INSERT INTO wp_nwm_posts VALUES("19799","1","2014-10-05 21:10:13","2014-10-05 21:10:13","espnW is a voice for the woman who loves sports. Founded in July 2010, espnW lives across television, films, events, digital and social platforms.
To connect with the W audience on a deeper digital level by building brand awareness and loyalty throughout the summer, an integrated social media campaign was created. 98 Days To Shine put the fans in the spotlight from Memorial Day to Labor Day via daily photo challenges, DIY projects, motivational quotes and athlete integration.
Participants were encouraged to check out Twitter or Instagram for the daily challenge, post their photo and tag it with #98DaysToShine. Facebook and Pinterest were used for additional amplification.
espnW featured participants photos on their website, espnW.com. Winners were awarded branded t-shirts and iPods and one-on-one Google+ hangouts with sponsoring pro athletes. The grand prize winner participated in all 98 challenges and earned trip to NYC to attend the US Open.
Results: 8,812 user generated photos were submitted during the 98-day campaign. The hashtag #98DaysToShine reached over 16 million social users. espnWs social footprint increased by 24% on Twitter and 7,500% on Instagram.
The achievements of the 98 Days to Shine photo challenge were celebrated with the Summer of W Finale event, a gallery showcase featuring the best entries from the photo challenge in the heart of NYCs NoLIta district.","espnW","Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Nam cursus. Morbi ut mi. Nullam enim leo, egestas id, condimentum at, laoreet mattis, massa.","inherit","open","open","","163-autosave-v1","","","2014-10-05 21:10:13","2014-10-05 21:10:13","","163","http://www.nicolemillerartdirector.com/?p=19799","0","revision","","0");
