INSERT INTO wp_nwm_posts VALUES("19957","1","2014-12-16 17:58:01","2014-12-16 17:58:01","[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" type=\"grid\" text_align=\"left\" padding_top=\"65\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_bottom=\"65\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"arrow_back\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<strong>EXPERIENCE</strong>
<hr />
&nbsp;
<strong>Associate Creative Director/Art Director 2013-Present</strong>
<em>Gardner Nelson + Partners New York, NY</em>
Darden Restaurant Group, Optimum, Little Trees Car Freshener, Assured Guaranty, Garanimals, Charter Communications, National Grid and new business.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\"][vc_column_text]<strong>Associate Creative Director/Art Director 2011-2013</strong>
<em>The Concept Farm New York, NY</em>
SC Johnson, Allstate Insurance, Ad Council, Aruba Tourism, espnW, Capital G Bank, ESPN co-branding with GMC, Miller Lite, Progressive and Chevy, and new business.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" up=\"10\" down=\"10\"][vc_column_text]<strong>Senior Art Director2006-2011</strong>
<em>The Concept Farm New York, NY</em>
ESPN co-branding with GMC, Cisco, Denny\'s, Craftsman, Wendy\'s and KFC, ESPN Wide World of Sports, American Heart Association, Disney, espnW, Greenpeace, American Greetings, Cartoon Network, The Bank of New York Mellon, National Women\'s Law Center, Capital G, Windstream Communications, and new business.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" up=\"10\" down=\"10\"][vc_column_text]<strong>Art Director Intern 2005</strong>
<em>Crispin Porter + Bogusky Boulder, CO</em>
Virgin Airlines, Miller Light, Burger King, Haggar Clothing, Hoopla[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" up=\"10\" down=\"10\" position=\"center\"][vc_column_text]<strong>Art Director Student Intern 2005</strong>
<em>Saatchi&amp;Saatchi, Leo Burnett, Y&amp;R: London,UK</em>
Toyota, Carlsberg, New Zealand Tourism, NSPCC, Glacier[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" up=\"45\" down=\"10\" position=\"center\"][vc_column_text]<strong>AWARDS</strong>
<hr />
&nbsp;
<strong>Emmy</strong>. <em>TV PSA Campaign. American Heart Association.</em>
<strong>Bronze Effie Award.</strong> <em>Aruba Tourism.</em>
<strong>Silver Obie.</strong> <em>Traditional Billboard Campaign. Ad Council.</em>
<strong>Shorty Industry Awards Finalist.</strong> <em>Best Use of Social Media for Sports. espnW</em>
<strong>Ad Age Campaign of the Year - Digital</strong>. <em>Small Agency Awards. Silver. espnW.</em>
<strong>IAC Awards.</strong> <em>Outstanding Website. ESPN Wide World of Sports.</em>
<strong>Platinum Pixie</strong>. <em>Motion Effects. Windstream Communications</em>.
<strong>Gold Magellan Award.</strong> <em>Web Marketing/Advertising. Aruba Tourism.</em>
<strong>Gold Magellan Award.</strong> <em>Overall Destinations - Family Destination. Aruba Tourism.</em>
<strong>6 Assorted Financial Communication Awards.</strong> <em>Campaign. Assured Guaranty.</em>
<strong>2 Gold Financial Communications Awards.</strong><em> Print and TV. BNYMellon.</em>
<strong>4 Addys.</strong> <em>National and Local. Student Work.</em>
<strong>Junior Olympic Diver of the Year.</strong> <em>11 and under.Springboard Diving.</em>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]<strong>ABOUT</strong>
<hr />
&nbsp;
I\'ll save you my list of fun facts, quirky jobs and countries I\'ve visitedwritten in third person. To paint a picture of what it was like to work with me, here it is. I\'m on time 99% of the time. Persuading people to help me deliver the best work possible without being a jerk comes naturally. I\'m a talker and a doer.Small groups, strong relationships and being elbows deep in an agency and a brand (or three) is where I thrive. That requires hard work, initiative, photoshop skills and type-A-like tendencies. My fight is to craftmemorable creative communications without losing their integrity through the tumbler of client feedback, budget restrictions, research, timing, politics and other unpredictable forces. I believe with the kind of hours we keep doing this, it\'s important to laugh a lot and pet animals.
&nbsp;
