<hr />
&nbsp;
<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">I\'ll save you my list of fun facts, quirky jobs and countries I\'ve visited, written in third person. To paint a picture of what it was like to work with me, here it is. I\'m on time 99% of the time. Persuading people to help me deliver the best work possible without being a jerk comes naturally. I\'m a talker and a doer. Small groups, strong relationships and being elbows deep in an agency and a brand (or three) is where I thrive. I fight to craft memorable creative without losing it\'s integrity through the tumbler of client feedback, budget restrictions, research, timing, politics and other unpredictable forces. That requires hard work, initiative, lots of hats, photoshop skillz and type-A-like tendencies. I believe with the kind of hours we keep doing this, it\'s important to laugh a lot and pet animals.?</span>
