INSERT INTO wp_nwm_posts VALUES("20135","1","2015-03-05 12:23:52","2015-03-05 12:23:52","<p>Assured Guaranty is a municipal bond insurer. In their foray into TV advertising, they wanted to communicate their air-tight guarantee in a way that was unexpected for the financial services catagory. The campaign that supported these broadcast TV spots, featured pre-roll videos and companion banners with a polling mechanism. This campaign earned us 6 Financial Communication Society Awards.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>After the success of their first TV campaign, in 2015, AG sought to shift the focus of its television advertising from a brand-awareness orientation to more product-benefit advertising, centered on conveying the core benefit of bond insurance. We developed a metaphorical spot that emphasizes the confidence an investor feels when his bonds are insured by Assured Guaranty - one of the safest investments on Wall Street.</p>
